    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>fresh</strong> <strong>tagliatelle</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>tagliatelle</strong> for 3-4 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> tagliatelle</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p>",
