      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>,<strong> dried oregano </strong>and<strong> balsamic vinegar</strong> with 80ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [100ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [130ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
